        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Cut the<strong> red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop ﬁnely</p><p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
