      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the burgers are cooking, add the<strong> chopped coriander</strong> and<strong> parsley</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> with the <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Grind to a paste, then stir through the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>,<strong> chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>chimichurri salsa</strong></p><p>Tip: Alternatively blitz it all together in a food processor!</p>",
